        <mxCell id="note-f2" value="Flujo Fase 2 (GSE):&#10;&#10;7. gse-cycle-init lee manifest → crea STATIONs + REQUESTs → notifica Signal Handler&#10;8. Signal Handler entrega payload a cada Agent. Agents extraen muestras → gse-raw&#10;9. SQS → Anonymizer lee gse-raw → transforma → escribe gse-anonymized&#10;10. gse-station-status cierra STATION cuando barrier met:&#10;     samples_anonymized + samples_skipped >= samples_expected&#10;11. gse-enterprise-status cierra CYCLE → notifica LLM Process Queue" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFF9C4;strokeColor=#FBC02D;fontColor=#5D4037;fontSize=13;align=left;verticalAlign=top;strokeWidth=2;spacingLeft=12;spacingTop=10;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="5400" y="1900" width="1280" height="200" as="geometry" />
